headlines.description: — Cade Cunningham scored 12 of his 22 points in the first quarter to help Detroit build a double-digit lead and he finished with eight assists in a 114-97 win over the <a...
headlines.shortLinkText: Cade Cunningham's 22 points, 8 assists help Pistons top Hornets 114-97 to take 3-game season series

headlines.description: — Kevin Durant scored 37 points and Devin Booker had 27 in his return from a right ankle sprain, rallying the Phoenix Suns to a 117-111 victory over the injury-depleted Cleveland Cavaliers on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kevin Durant scores 37 points, rallying Suns to 117-111 victory over Cavaliers

headlines.description: — Luka Doncic came through with yet another triple-double. About the only thing he didn't do was keep his record streak going.
headlines.shortLinkText: Doncic scores 27 but 30-point triple-double streak ends as Mavericks dominate Bulls 127-92

events.name: Golden State Warriors at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — Jonathan Kuminga scored 21 points, Klay Thompson added 20 and the Golden State Warriors overcame a sluggish start to beat the San Antonio Spurs 112-102 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kuminga, Thompson help Warriors rebound to upend Spurs 112-102 despite Wembanyama's strong return

headlines.description: — Jamal Murray scored 12 of his 26 points in the fourth quarter, and the Denver Nuggets rallied from 21 points down in the third quarter to beat the depleted Toronto Raptors 125-119 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jokic has 21st triple-double to rally Nuggets past depleted Raptors, 125-119

events.name: Boston Celtics at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — The Boston Celtics aren't taking 50 wins this season for granted.
headlines.shortLinkText: Brown has 27 and Tatum adds 26 for the Celtics in 121-99 win over Portland
